{
  "texts": [
    "Among these, VAEs have garnered considerable attention, and were the first architecture specifically applied to drug generation in 2017 (5).",
    "Subsequent studies have reinforced their utility and applicability (7, 8).",
    "VAEs function through a dual neural network architecture, comprised of an encoder that maps molecular structures into a latent space, and a decoder that reverses this transformation.",
    "Models have been designed to accommodate both 2D and 3D molecular representations (64).",
    "The PASITHEA model introduced \"deep dreaming\" to molecular design (65)."
  ]
}